    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo specifies the Common Profile for Presence (CPP) Presence Information Data Format (PIDF) as a common presence data format for CPP-compliant Presence protocols, and also defines a new media type "application/pidf+xml" to represent the XML MIME entity for PIDF. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
